Regulatory Information
It is important that you read this as it explains certain legal and regulatory restrictions applicable to the investment services we provide.
This website is not intended for any use, which would be contrary to the law or regulation of the place in which you live. In particular, this website is not aimed at persons who are residents of any country where the investment services and products described or referred to in this website are not registered or approved for marketing and sale or in which the dissemination of information about them is not permitted.
This website and its contents are neither intended nor able to sell services or products over the Internet. They are only for the convenience and information of internet viewers.
This website does not constitute an offer or solicitation by anyone in any jurisdiction in which such offer or solicitation is not lawful or in which the person making such offer or solicitation is not qualified to do so or to anyone to whom it is unlawful to make such offer or solicitation.
Veritas Investment Management LLP is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority in the conduct of its investment business. It is registered under number 584098. For more information click on www.fca.org.uk. The registered address of Veritas Investment Management LLP is 90 Long Acre, London, WC2E 9RA.
Veritas Investment Management AG, the associate company of Veritas Investment Management LLP, is incorporated in Switzerland and is a member of the Swiss Association of Asset Managers. It is not an authorised person under the UK Financial Services and Markets Act 2000. Accordingly, the protections provided by the UK regulatory system do not apply to the operations of Veritas Investment Management AG described in this brochure and customers of Veritas Investment Management AG will not be protected by the UK Investors Compensation Scheme.
Advice
Veritas does not offer investment advice on the merits or suitability of the funds described in this website and no information contained within this website should be construed as such. If you are in doubt, you should seek advice from a professional financial adviser.
Risk Warnings

Past performance is not a guide to future performance.
The value of investments and the income from them may fluctuate and are not guaranteed.
Investors may not get back the whole amount they have invested.
Changes in rates of exchange between currencies may cause the value of investments to diminish or to increase.

